<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>About Us - Our Store</title>
  <style>

    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #555;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 0;
    }
    section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
      color: #444;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #e67e22;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      border-left: 5px solid #e67e22;
      border-right: 5px solid #e67e22;
      background-color: #fff3e0;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .why-choose-us {
      margin-top: 50px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .section-subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #666;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .features {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .feature-item {
      flex: 1 1 45%;
      background-color: #fff8f0;
      border: 2px solid #e67e22;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(230, 126, 34, 0.15);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    .feature-item:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(230, 126, 34, 0.3);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 40px;
      color: #e67e22;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
      text-align: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .features {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .feature-item {
        flex: 1 1 100%;
      }
      header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      section p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>About Our Store</h1>
      <p>Your trusted source for quality products</p>
    </header>
    <section>
      <p>Welcome to <span class="highlight">Our Store</span>, where quality meets affordability. Founded in 2020, we have dedicated ourselves to providing a wide range of products that meet your everyday needs with an emphasis on excellent customer service.</p>
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To offer you not just products, but solutions that simplify your life. Whether you're looking for the latest gadgets, home essentials, or unique gifts, we have something for you.</p>
      </div>
      <p>With over 10,000 satisfied customers and growing, we're committed to continuous improvement and innovation in our product offerings.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="why-choose-us">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Here's what makes us different</p>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-item" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Premium Quality">
          <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">üíé</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Premium Quality</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Every product is carefully selected to meet our high standards of quality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Best Prices">
          <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">üí∞</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Best Prices</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">We offer competitive pricing without compromising on quality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Great Customer Support">
          <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">ü§ù</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Great Customer Support</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Our friendly support team is here to help you with any questions or concerns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Fast and Reliable Shipping">
          <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">üöö</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Fast and Reliable Shipping</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">We ensure your orders arrive on time and in perfect condition.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>